            "failure_message": "Approach-oriented anticipation with engagement + arousal + enough control to feel ready (not helpless), and not hostile/detached. Interest is the default hook; lonely-yearning or romantic-yearning can also supply the 'charged waiting' tone. Excludes fear-freeze and stays well below panic; change-gate can be anticipation crossing/spike, engagement jump, or a lonely-yearning surge (still requires anticipation >= 0.6)."
